name: Twisted Paradise Revelation
description:
SOUND ON

What happend ?

You don't know, but you've been falling down in the darkness for hours or even days everything is blurry.

Your eyes are used to the darkness, that's why you saw it instantly.

The light is so bright it reminds you of something, but you don't know what.

Your body is reacting to the angelic light, cold shivers and sweat, you're whole body is shaking.

Is it your first time here ?

Maybe not after all.

What is this place ?

Something isn't right.

It seems so beautiful you want to get closer, after all what's worst than eternal darkness, you can get into paradise.

AI Generated Piece of 500 steps in 1024*768p turned in a video, this piece is inspired by Dante and the Divine Comedy, here it's my never ending limbo where everything is twisted.

Reach for me on Twitter with a proof of ownership and I'll sent you the steps.
